replyContent: Thank you for updating your review! Some phones (xiaomi for example) will change the in-app font color when 'dark mode' is selected which leads to unreadable text (white text on white background) - that's why we lock the theme. We will keep an eye on this issue and maybe provide an override to disable darkmode in the settings in future versions.

replyContent: Like most other currency converters we are using international mid-market rates (the median of international buy and sell rates).
